name: Keep an Eye
description: Help strange creatures to bring the eye to a mysterious customer through 18 levels of this intuitive but hardcore physical puzzle game

name: Giraffe Hero
description: The Giraffe is trying to release his friends, help him become a hero and throw stones and bombs till they all be free.

name: Run Red Run
description: OMG! the wolf is here to make a breakfast out of Red! Help her run as far as she can, collect the apples and use the super upgrades on your way

name: Free Fred
description: Fred the dolphin was your best friend while you were a kid, till some bad guys came and took him. Now, you are old enough to go out after them and release your friend. Go out, upgrade your ship and fight.

name: Fifish
description: Fifish is our friendly fish, he just saw a cell phone that he really wants, but, it costs 23 pearls... Can you help our friend to find the hidden pearls and buy himself a nice new cellphone?

name: Mr Gunface
description: Beautifully rendered and epic arena shooter, 16 upgradeable weapons, 25 Enemies, 6 Unique Bosses and 30 stages to fight through

name: The Right Way
description: The little robot can only walk straight forwards or, right. Help him get to the exit in each and every level.

name: Mummy Buster
description: it seems that the mummies are not really dead yet,kill all of the mummies by guiding them to their death.

name: Go Robots
description: The robots have to go to their bases. Help them do so in a fun puzzle/mind game.

name: Car Yard
description: You are a little car, on your way to the cars yard. Your target - stay alive, do not get crushed. Can you do it? how fast can you do it?

name: Cheese Barn
description: The mouse is hungry! Can you help him get his favorite cheese? Play a fun puzzle/mind game. More levels on the AppStore and Google.Play

name: Polkafriz
description: It's the Ice Age! But it will get hotter soon! Follow a cute girl named Ern, to stop the Polkafriz (the mountain chains) from erupting!

name: SmashZ
description: Big Bob is here to save and end the apocalypse! Grab any object and drop it on top of Zombies head! A fun physics game that everybody will love. Get ready for this head smashing game!

name: Transmyter
description: Your name is Ezzy. You are a metamorf from the planet Kastella-6. You can turn into anything around you. After the crash on this weird planet you've lost your girlfriend Smoorfy.

name: How to make a Suquel
description: Save your cows, don't let them go away in a funny puzzle game. Guide your cow to the exit, pay attention to the instructions in each and every level.

name: Pick and Dig 3
description: Pick and Dig is back, help the pink hero to collect the money and the diamonds. Solve the puzzle on his way

name: Hippo the Brave Knight
description: Hippo, the brave night is going out to his greatest adventure of his life, he has to rescue the kingdom and get back home safe. Please help him accomplish that mission.

name: Splitman 2
description: Sequel to the popular clones stacking platformer puzzle game. A total of 30 levels. 6 are bonus unlockable levels by collecting hard to reach KeyCards scattered throughout the levels. Can you reach the exit on every level???

name: Simple Motions 2
description: Control the creature collecting stars along the way and reach the red flag to complete the level. 35 levels of fun physics game, plan your route and win the game.

name: Cut The Monster
description: No one likes monsters! here you have a chance to cut them using lasers. Play that fun physics games with puzzle elements using your mouse

name: Toilet Success
description: A game with story about perseverance, courage and success! A very unique philosophical game that will leave you light and happy!

name: I saw her standing there
description: I saw her standing there, but then she was a.... You will have to play to find that out :) Play a fun minimal platform puzzle game.

name: Clutch Burn
description: A super addictive racing game. Loads of premium content. unique scenery, unlockable upgrades, autosaving system. smooth balanced gameplay. It's just a real fun and well made game. - 4 stunning tracks which are unique,

name: Be Ready
description: Play a mouse only game where you have to save the queen! Will you succeed to do it and win all of the other ninjas and enemies on your way?

name: Starcede
description: Shoot your way through the galaxy, leaving behind a trail of destruction and awesomeness

name: Run 2 Live - Great Escape
description: Run for your life! Upgrade yourself and try to pass all of the levels in a great unique game

name: Doctor Acorn
description: Join Dr. Acorn in his second adventure. Hill the birds using the hidden pills which you have to collect during the game and bring the doctor back home as fast as you can

name: Golden Intuition
description: Play a fun mini-game, how far can you get without falling or being override by the giant rocks?

name: On The Wheels
description: Pick your car, write your name and go out racing. a fun racing game where you have to collect the money, upgrade your car and finish the race

name: Angel of the Battlefield
description: When the time get tough, the tough get going. Help the wounded rabbits! The battlefield is full with wounded rabbits, only one angel can save them. be that angel and get the rabbits to the tent

name: Robots cant Think
description: Can Robots think? It seems they cannot. You will have to think and solve the puzzle in this fun action game/platformer.

name: Cat around Asia
description: Our hungry cat continues its trip around the world and now it got to Asia! Help the cute cat get his food.

name: Zombudoy
description: Hungry zombies are coming for your food! You have to defend your food and shoot all of those zombies

name: Another Planet 2
description: The cute alien is back, help him get to the exit in each level

name: Paint World 2 Monsters
description: The monsters torn the paint world apart, help the paint guys to get it back together.

name: Paper Venture 2
description: After escaping from the pit, tiny alien sucked himself into a portal and now stuck in another new world full of dangers and you need to help him to get out of there.

name: Parking Hooligan 2
description: The Parking Hooligan is back! Play the funny parking game where you should destroy EVERYTHING! Do not leave any object in place, it is the Parking Hooligan 2!

name: Pain Tiger
description: Mad platformer in which your goal - hurt myself, but not to collect various goodies! Play that crazy game and see if you can win it.

name: Speedway Challenge
description: Select your favorite driver, buy the most expensive car that you can and go on to the speedway challenge in a great car racing game.

name: Hell On Duty
description: Fun cannon shooting game with ragdolls and 60 levels! Help hell inhabitants to get all demons into boilers.

name: Super Sub Hero
description: Guide a scared little Eskimo boy through a series of puzzles on a quest to save his grandpa. Super Sub Hero is a cute and cheerful puzzle platform game with a bit different mechanics.
